---
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Copyright & Permissions | Father's Heart Bible™"
  description="Copyright, ownership, and permission to quote the Father's Heart Bible™ — an original translation published and owned by Spirit Media Publishing, the imprint of Spirit Media Inc."
  jsonLd={{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://fathersheartbible.com/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Copyright & Permissions", "item": "https://fathersheartbible.com/copyright" }
    ]
  }}
>

  <main id="main-content" style="margin-top: 80px;">
    <Section variant="soft">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light mb-6" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-ink);">Copyright &amp; Permissions</h1>

        <p class="text-base mb-8 leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-ink); font-family: var(--font-sans);">
          <strong>Holy Bible, Father's Heart Bible™, copyright &copy; 2026 by Spirit Media Publishing, the imprint of Spirit Media Inc. All rights reserved.</strong>
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-8" style="font-family: var(--font-sans); color: var(--color-muted);">

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-ink);">Ownership</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">Father's Heart Bible™ is an original English translation from the original Hebrew, Aramaic, and Greek, published and owned by <a href="https://spiritmediapublishing.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Spirit Media Publishing</a>, the imprint of Spirit Media Inc., founded by Kevin and Shelly White. Kevin White led the translation and publishing process. First published June 21, 2026, online at fathersheartbible.com; print editions followed July 4, 2026. This is the First Edition (2026), a living text.</p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed" style="margin-top: 12px;">For the story and the method behind the translation, read the <a href="/the-fathers-heart-bible/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Preface and A Note on the Translation</a>.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-ink);">Quoting the Father's Heart Bible™</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">The Father's Heart Bible™ text may be quoted in any form (written, visual, electronic, or audio) up to and inclusive of <strong>five hundred (500) verses</strong> without express written permission, provided the verses quoted do not amount to a complete book of the Bible, nor account for more than <strong>twenty-five percent (25%)</strong> of the total text of the work in which they are quoted.</p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-3">When quoting, one of the following credit lines must appear on the copyright page or title page of the work:</p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-3 p-4" style="background: var(--color-surface-lowest, #f5f0e8); border-radius: 8px;">Scripture quotations are taken from the Father's Heart Bible™, copyright &copy; 2026 by Spirit Media Publishing. Used by permission. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">When quotations are used in non-salable media — such as church bulletins, orders of service, newsletters, or projected slides — a complete copyright notice is not required, but the initials <strong>FHB</strong> must appear at the end of each quotation. Quotations in excess of five hundred (500) verses or twenty-five percent (25%) of the work, and any commercial use of the FHB text in a commentary or other Bible-reference work, require written permission (see below).</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-ink);">Trademarks</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">Father's Heart Bible™, FHB, the Father's Heart Bible logo, and ComfortLeather™ are trademarks of Spirit Media Inc.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-ink);">Permission requests</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">For permission requests beyond the allowance above, and for bulk-purchase inquiries, contact Spirit Media Publishing at <a href="mailto:publisher@spiritmediapublishing.com" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">publisher@spiritmediapublishing.com</a>.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>
  </main>
</Layout>
